        <abstract> 
<p>Many of EB’s remarks about <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> [4th ed. (1866)] are new to CD.</p> 
            <p>Thinks of writing a short essay on man.</p>
            <p>Struck by EB’s remarks about orang. They are similar to Carl Vogt’s remarks on origin of man from distinct ape families.</p>
            <p>Thinks similarity of orang to Malay must be accidental.</p> 
<p>Will send <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> when it is published.</p> 
        </abstract>
